{"tid":2501330,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國3月零售數據好過預期　按月升5.4%","createTime":"2021-04-23T09:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T09:42:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4472bbc79a13bf6d3e66977f3c765350f19b6dd3","tid":2501330,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587348-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587348-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9fgUEJ%2BH4pM5xz2q5iffzskuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=59d062a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587348-20210423.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=8b60a2e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587348-20210423.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國3月零售數據好過預期。<br />\n<br />\n英國國家統計局公布，3月零售銷售按月增加5.4%，大幅好過市場預期的增長1.5%，按年增加7.2%，亦好過預期的3.5%。<br />\n<br />\n上月扣除能源的零售銷售按月增加4.9%，按年增加7.9%，兩者都顯著好過預期，市場原本估計分別增加1.9%及4.5%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，英國3月扣除國有銀行的公共部門淨借款為280億英鎊，多於預期。"}]}